{
  "stem": "8191.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went to see the Hamadan, and I went to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I looked and I looked and I looked, and I find-- [LAUGHS] I find a grave by the name Haman.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's how I associate Hamadan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I became allergic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, the water in that time used to come from the mountains when the snow melt-- melted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And anything that I touched in that time smelled with lamb and mutton.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I had a contract for two years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that was the first six months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Whatever I-- whatever I touched, even caviar-- [INAUDIBLE] the bread smells for lamb or mutton.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they let me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They said, go out and-- so the doctor advised me to go to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in [INAUDIBLE], in-- from Damascus.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's high in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They said, go spend two or three weeks, whatever you want, and come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maybe you'll make a change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I spent there three weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I came back to-- to Iran, and the same thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I couldn't-- so they let me out in November, in '38.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I went back to Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in '38.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also I had an assignment from-- from the French government to-- when the war broke out with Spain, with Franco, a year and a half later, England and France declared a blockade against Spain.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was-- and all the Spaniards, that they came back after the fall of Madrid, they were living in a camp in Perpignan.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the camp, the name of the little town was Rivesaltes.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
